# Blue - TryHackMe Writeup

**Platform:** TryHackMe  
**OS:** Windows 7 Professional SP1  
**Difficulty:** Easy  
**Date:** April 2026  

---

## Machine Info

A classic Windows machine demonstrating one of the most famous vulnerabilities in history — EternalBlue (MS17-010). No web server, no rabbit holes. Pure network exploitation.

---

## Enumeration

### Nmap Scan

```bash
nmap -sC -sV 10.49.156.70
```

```
